  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Source</strong> <em>Ultimate Equipment pg. 117</em>, <em>PRPG Core Rulebook pg. 463</em></p><p><strong>Aura</strong> faint abjuration <strong>CL</strong> 3rd</p><p><strong>Slot</strong> armor/shield quality; <strong>Price</strong> +18,000 gp; <strong>Weight</strong> -</p><p><h3 class=\"framing\"><img src=\"modules/pf-content/assets/PathfinderSocietySymbol.gif\" title=\"PFS Legal\" style=\"margin:3px 3px 0px 3px;\"><strong>Description</strong></h3>A suit of armor or a shield with this special ability protects against one type of energy (acid, cold, electricity, fire, or sonic) and is designed with patterns depicting the element it protects against. The armor absorbs the first 10 points of energy damage per attack that the wearer would normally take (similar to the <em>resist energy </em>spell).</p><p><h3 class=\"framing\"><strong>Construction</strong></h3><strong>Requirements</strong> Craft Magic Arms and Armor, <em>resist energy</em>; <strong>Price</strong> +9,000 gp</p>",
